{"tid":2338651,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"與王菲有望同台丨鍾欣潼為張栢芝拒《乘風破浪的姐姐》邀請 免得被舊事重提","createTime":"2020-12-24T06:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T11:35:29.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c01947797123cd23bfc245ba8ed226108c35e3e0","tid":2338651,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:52:33.000Z","msg":"王菲、張栢芝和謝霆鋒這段關係糾纏了20年，王菲與霆鋒在1999年突然爆出姊弟戀，當時兩人戀得火熱之際，在2002年因為栢芝的介入而分手，其後霆鋒與栢芝結婚並生了兩個仔，而王菲亦嫁了給李亞鵬，不過最後兩人各自與另一半離婚，最終兩人在2014年世紀復合，相戀至今。<br />\n<br />\n雖然當時栢芝曾經祝福對前夫與舊愛世紀復合，不過仍然「花生友」期望他們有同台的一日，近日有傳張栢芝將會那英、容祖兒、陳妍希、周筆暢、董潔和王鷗等人參加大陸的綜藝節目《乘風破浪的姐姐》，有傳因為王菲是節目贊助品牌的代言人，加上與那英又份屬好友，於是傳出王菲將會為節目主題曲，這對昔日情敵有望同台。另一方面，今日亦有台灣傳媒報道，本來劇組曾經邀請鍾欣潼（阿嬌）助陣，但因為栢芝的關係而婉拒了。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201224/AFAW4T6DSBD43I3SGZFCQ4RKWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201224%2FAFAW4T6DSBD43I3SGZFCQ4RKWA%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76McLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=99822d40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201224%2FAFAW4T6DSBD43I3SGZFCQ4RKWA%2F&h=4a6f455c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201224/AFAW4T6DSBD43I3SGZFCQ4RKWA/</a>"},{"pid":"7ccd8e30302163c61dd4e413a9b1dfd4e9ff2536","tid":2338651,"uid":149494,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:57:04.000Z","msg":"容祖兒乜撚狗屎垃圾都上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301ffd8fbc5f0c88184205731b425e856faf158c","tid":2338651,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T06:57:43.000Z","msg":"希仔，黑鮑，bobo<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\